assertion_line: 38
expression: "get_subcommand_help(\"policy\")"
---
View and manage policy rules

Usage: policy <COMMAND>

Commands:
  list      List rules in the active policy
  validate  Validate policy files and report errors
  edit      Open the interactive policy editor (or $EDITOR with --raw)
  allow     Add an allow rule for a tool or binary
  deny      Add a deny rule for a tool or binary
  remove    Remove a rule matching a tool or binary
  help      Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help
